A little difficult to get the hang of at first, but once you work out what you're doing it has a lot of depth and, I think, replay value. A couple of tips: try to play the types of stores in order as you will need to unlock recipes and items for later stores from the base stores. Also don't be afraid to use the replay data created at the end of each year to start new games frequently - items, unlocked recipes and your manager's stats carry over!
